kbd-auto-layout (1.5.0) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Add service lifecycle commands: enable, disable, restart.
  * Improve use-current-keyboard selection and ambiguity messages.
  * Add rule specificity scoring and ambiguity warnings.
  * Improve explain output with rule scoring.
  * Keep GNOME Wayland backend explicit and improve doctor guidance.
  * Use Debian-compatible unstable distribution in changelog.

