kbd-auto-layout (1.3.0) stable; urgency=medium

  * Add event-driven input monitoring using udevadm.
  * Add automatic fallback to polling when event monitoring is unavailable.
  * Add event mode and event timeout configuration.
  * Improve daemon responsiveness for keyboard hotplug events.

